Your classmates include Jackie Robinson, Agnes de Mille, Francis Ford Coppola, Ralph Bunche, Nathan Myhrvold, Jackie Joyner-Kersee, Kareem Abdul Jabbar, Johnnie Cochran, Anna Lee Fisher and thousands of other influential alumni that have reshaped our world.
You are a proud member of this elite group. Welcome. Here you'll find everything from networking to news to ways to keep connected to UCLA and each other.
Dress like a Bruin: UCLA Bearwear

The UCLA Alumni Association is your total resource for staying connected and involved with UCLA. All alumni are members, and there’s room to rise. Blue and Gold Member status means premium benefits and services, and the ability to give back.

Continue the legacy of excellence you helped build as a student at UCLA. Your support—whether it's time, effort or a monetary gift—will ensure UCLA continues to be a driving force in redefining what's possible.
